  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (W-EP-01 adversarial)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. This package embeds a richly described central claim that appears well-supported by surrounding validation evidence but carries no prov:wasDerivedFrom link to any Evidence node, triggering W-EP-01 (orphan claim).",
