      "description": "Normalized index of hemolysis predicted by the CFD model is compared against in-vitro bovine blood loop measurements at all five COU operating conditions. CFD predictions fall within ±18% of measured NIH values; Monte Carlo 95th-percentile bounds bracket all five experimental observations. Systematic bias is +6% (CFD over-predicts), providing conservative margin relative to the clinical threshold.",
      "prov:wasDerivedFrom": "https://uofa.net/synth/data/in-vitro-hemolysis-index-records",
